Package: diffUTR
Type: Package
Title: diffUTR: Streamlining differential exon and 3' UTR usage
Version: 0.99.2
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Authors@R: c(
	person("Pierre-Luc", "Germain", email="pierre-luc.germain@hest.ethz.ch", role=c("cre","aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3418-4218")), 
	person("Stefan", "Gerber", email="gerberst@student.ethz.ch", role="aut") )
Description: Provides a uniform interface and plotting functions for limma/edgeR/DEXSeq -powered differential exon usage, 
	as well as their application to differential UTR usage analysis using poly-A site databases. Includes in addition an
	improved version of the limma::diffSplice method.
Imports: S4Vectors, SummarizedExperiment, limma, edgeR, DEXSeq, GenomicRanges, SEtools, Rsubread, ggplot2, rtracklayer, ComplexHeatmap, ggrepel, stringi, methods, stats
Suggests: BiocStyle, knitr
biocViews: GeneExpression
VignetteBuilder: knitr
